Joined and flat version of EDI data package knb-lter-mcm.9003.11

Source: R/data.R
hymet_L0_flat.Rd

A fully joined and flat version of EDI data package knb-lter-mcm.9003.11 (Seasonal high-frequency measurements of discharge, water temperature, and specific conductivity from Andersen Creek at H1, McMurdo Dry Valleys, Antarctica (1993-2020, ongoing)) with all relevant hymetDP L1 identifiers and content added. Use this dataset as an input to the L0_flat argument of the "create" functions.

hymet_L0_flat

Format

A data frame with 30,000 rows and 45 variables:

LocalDateTime

Local datetime

UTCOffset

Local timezone offset from UTC

DateTimeUTC

Datetime in UTC

variable_name

Variable name from the L0 dataset

DataValue

Numeric value of the observation

Qualifier

Code of a qualifier (flag)

unit

Unit name from the L0 dataset

ValueID

The data value ID

VariableCode

The variable ID

VariableName

The ODM CV variable name

VariableUnitsName

The ODM CV unit name for the variable

SampleMedium

The ODM CV sample medium name

ValueType

The ODM CV value type

IsRegular

Whether the values are from a regularly sampled dataset

TimeSupport

Temporal footprint of samples

TimeUnitsName

The ODM CV unit name for time support

DataType

The ODM CV data type

GeneralCategory

The ODM CV general category

NoDataValue

The numeric value used to encode not available data

MethodCode

The method ID

MethodDescription

The description of the method

SiteCode

The site ID

SiteName

The name of the site

Latitude

Latitude of site

Longitude

Longitude of site

Elevation_m

Elevation of site in meters

SiteType

The ODM CV site type

Organization

Name of organization that collected the data

ContactName

Name of contact person for the data source

Email

Email of contact

SourceCode

The source ID

SourceDescription

The description of the source data

SourceLink

URL of source data

Citation

Citation for the source data

Phone

Contact phone

Address

Contact physical address

City

Contact city

State

Contact state if in US, otherwise full country name

ZipCode

Contact postal code

QualityControlLevelCode

The quality control ID

Definition

Definition of the quality control level

Explanation

Explanation of the quality control level

QualifierCode

The qualifier ID

QualifierDescription

Description of the qualifier

Source

https://portal.edirepository.org/nis/mapbrowse?scope=knb-lter-mcm&identifier=9003&revision=11
